text: Boarnsterhim () is a former municipality in the Dutch province of Friesland. On 1 January 2014, the municipality was dissolved and its territory was split between four other municipalities: De Fryske Marren, which was created that day, Leeuwarden, Heerenveen and Súdwest-Fryslân.
